  "rationale": "Tier C substrate crate from plans/2026-06-22-phenotype-ecosystem-router-architecture-v1.md. Exercises all three execution lanes (sync, fanout, tree) provided by substrate::wave against in-memory stub engines + engine-agentapi (offline mode). Gates the worktree at the type-system boundary so future lane refactors break the build rather than silently degrade.",
  "test_names": [
    "sync_lane_start_post_message_dump_completes",
    "fanout_lane_dispatches_to_all_engines_with_partial_failure",
