    "fanout_lane_semaphore_bounds_concurrency",
    "tree_lane_a2a_task_tree_correlates_events",
    "sync_lane_conformance_suite_passes_for_engine_agentapi"
  ],
  "notes": "Hermetic by design — no network, no subprocess. Production paths are stubbed; integration with real engines (engine-agentapi, engine-claude, engine-codex, engine-forge) is verified via the conformance suite assertion in the last test."
